subject: Olympic Games (2008)
Track and Field
Olympic Games
lead_paragraph: Cuba’s Dayron Robles sailed cleanly over 10 hurdles with his left leg leading and never getting ahead of himself to win the men’s 110-meter hurdles convincingly in 12.93 seconds.
